Sheebla <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#414141><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bbrellserilis.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=ulver>Ulver</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Slackershaman</span><br>  Posts: 333<br> <font color=#CC9900>(4/27/01 8:58:05 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: re</span><hr size=1> What would you recommend? That when someone posts a reservation that they either say they are for or against someone helping with CT if he's up? That people cannot ask for help in a plane? That only the original guild that signed up for the plane can kill him at that date?<br>
<br>
Please, don't think this is a rant. But I think we have a lot of people saying what they do or do not like and not offering solutions. It seems like there are some differences in opinion here that compromise will be needed for. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#313532><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/utwiggietymberwolf.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Twiggie Tymberwolf</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Guardian of Underfoot</span><br>  Posts: 812<br> <font color=#CC9900>(4/27/01 9:14:12 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: re</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> Also, I find it unacceptable that the bosses are gone when I schedule a raid.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
