<br>
This last time SR/Watchers killed him the day was NOT SCHEDULED.  One other time they asked everyone that had fear scheduled for the next WEEK.  Do you really want to make it so that they have to schedule dates in Fear to kill him and then let all that armor that ALOT of people are fighting to get just rot?<br>
