__________<br>
<br>
And the only two mobs that should be considered here are CT and Draco.  Dread, Fright, and Terror can be taken down by a guild that knows what they are doing.  Harpers/SoTG took down all three with minimal losses.<br>
<br>
__________<br>
<br>
And no way should PoG be reserved in any way.  Twiggie is bound on the PoG tower and I go in there alot.  Its almost always full popped and empty of raiders.  Recently I hosted a few raids and now others on my raids have decided to host a few.  But the zone is still empty 6 out of 7 days a week or more. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#414141><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/usheebla1.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sheebla1</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Adventurer of Underfoot</span><br>  Posts: 49<br> <font color=#CC9900>(4/27/01 9:19:23 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   re</span><hr size=1> If you reserve the Plane, you have the right to all the mobs there.  If you can't take a mob, you leave it for the next raid who also has a right to that mob.  Now, if no one plans to take that mob, it's FFA or FCFA but, there has to be time alowed for a respawn for the raid that wants that mob.<br>
<br>
Yes, people will need to contact raid leaders and raid leaders will need to post their intentions.  An example would be as follows:  &quot;Ladies Home Sewing Circle guild doing Plane of Fear, we do not plan to take out any of the Bosses&quot;.  The bosses in this case are FFA or FCFS but will need to be killed with enough time to allow a respawn for the next reservation that does want the particular mobs.  It's just to simple and courtious to everyone.<br>
<br>
And, guilds get help from outside the guild all the time, I have been asked many time to go help out.  I just hope people understant that there are numerous guilds that can summon supplemental help.<br>
<br>
Sheebla <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#313532><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/usilverwreath.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Silverwreath</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Adventurer of Underfoot</span><br>  Posts: 31<br> <font color=#CC9900>(4/27/01 9:42:34 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Reservation System</span><hr size=1> I agree that the reserve system should be the whole plane. I also agree that PoG should be reserved like the other planes. <br>
<br>
<br>
I disagree on allowing help from other guilds on raid. (Maybe Im not understanding this point) But as a member of a small guild we need other guilds help in pulling off raids.  <br>
<br>
<br>
I also believe if we have it in place EVERYONE needs to follow it. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#414141><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/unasren.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Nasren</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Adventurer of Underfoot</span><br>  Posts: 88<br> <font color=#CC9900>(4/27/01 10:03:17 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Reservation System</span><hr size=1> I have been on a CT killing before the change. In that raid we got down to the end and then had more people show up in the plane in order to take down CT. These were not people that took place in the raid previously.<br>
<br>
Many fear raids in the past followed this exact same formula, you clear the plane up to the gods and then others show up to take down CT. At least for small guilds this was the case.<br>
<br>
They didn't simple pass CT along because that raid crew could not handle CT, they got others. The sought out higher numbers and higher lvls.<br>
<br>
How is this different from now? Guild A goes to fear, CT is up they go through killing everything they can then call up the reinforcements to take out CT on THEIR scheduled day.<br>
<br>
Are you upset because how the planes were done in the past and still done today is not acceptable to you or because you had a planed raid that comes 6 days and not 7 days after CT was killed and thus will not be up for you?<br>
<br>
I am deeply against any new reservations. Unless a solid reason can come up as to why a underutilized and very large plane like PoG should be added I can not see my view changing.<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#313532><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bbrellserilis.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=duffer>Duffer</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/image/globalBlack.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>I'm a little teapot....</span><br>  Posts: 544<br> <font color=#CC9900>(4/27/01 10:23:27 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Reservation System</span><hr size=1> <br>
